{
  "texts": [
    "Based on the literature on automatic plankton recognition various challenges can be identified.",
    "The most notable challenges are as follows:",
    "The amount of labeled data for training is limited.",
    "This challenge can be divided into two subchallenges: (1) expert knowledge is required for data labeling, and (2) certain plankton species are notably less common producing a small amount of example images.",
    "Plankton species are inherently difficult to identify, requiring prior expertise."
  ]
}